ged out.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub96.ezboard.com/usinafeykb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SiNafeyKB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Level 2, Generic Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/2/02 6:49:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub96.ezboard.com/fkanebaylecommunitycenterfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=543.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogues in Bazaar</span><hr size=1> HTML has been removed in the last patch.<br><br>Too bad... I was getting used to my yellow heal message. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub96.ezboard.com/unikedemus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nikedemus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Level 2, Generic Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/3/02 3:21:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub96.ezboard.com/fkanebaylecommunitycenterfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=543.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.strike9.com/file.aspx/path=/KacerRex/fullsize/fairy_bounce01.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogues in Bazaar</span><hr size=1> The pickpocket thing was only an issue on PvP servers, and pickpocketing has been disabled in the bazaar already. The /body thing got fixed last patch too. <p><center><b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=291962" target="_blank">Kagan Gnomepunter</a></b></center><center><b><a href="http://www.shattered-sorcery.com/iv/" target="_blank">In Virtue</a></b></center><center>